data.title: Visits by Foreign Leaders
data.text: President Ahidjo Presidential guest. Afterwards visited New York City. Departed U.S. March 18. March 13–15, 1962 President Ahmadou Ahidjo Informal visit. In U.S. October 19–25; visited New York City and Pittsburgh. October 24–25, 1967 President Ahmadou Ahidjo Private visit. October 9, 1969 President Ahmadou Ahidjo Official working visit. Private visit afterwards to Gainesville (Fla.). July 25–28, 1982 President Paul Biya Official Working Visit. Private visit to Los Angeles afterward. February 25–28, 1986 President Paul Biya Met with President Bush during a private visit. May 6, 1991 President Paul Biya Working visit. March 20–21, 2003 Prime Minister Peter Musonge Attended United States-Africa Business Summit; met with President Bush during a private visit June 26. June 22–29, 2003
